<% layout('layouts/boilerplate') -%>
<body>
    <div class="hero-section">
        <h1>About Us</h1>
        <p class="tagline">Your Gateway to Incredible India!</p>
    </div>

    <div class="container">
        <section class="welcome-section">
            <h2>Welcome to Tripnest</h2>
            <p>At Tripnest, we are passionate about connecting travelers with the rich, diverse, and vibrant experiences that only India can offer. From the snow-capped peaks of Himachal to the sun-soaked beaches of Goa, from the heritage-rich cities of Rajasthan to the lush greenery of Kerala, Tripnest is your one-stop destination for discovering the best stays across India.</p>
        </section>

        <section class="who-we-are">
            <h2>Who We Are</h2>
            <div class="content-box">
                <p>Tripnest is an Indian-born travel platform designed exclusively to help you explore only Indian locations and hotels. We understand the essence of Indian hospitality, and our platform reflects just that – warmth, tradition, comfort, and affordability. We aim to support local hotels and accommodations, promoting domestic tourism and helping you uncover hidden gems across the country.</p>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="what-we-offer">
            <h2>What We Offer</h2>
            <div class="features-grid">
                <div class="feature-card">
                    <i class="fas fa-hotel"></i>
                    <h3>Curated Stays</h3>
                    <p>Handpicked hotels, homestays, guesthouses, and resorts that reflect the true spirit of Indian culture and hospitality.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-card">
                    <i class="fas fa-map-marker-alt"></i>
                    <h3>India-Only Destinations</h3>
                    <p>Whether you're planning a peaceful retreat in the hills or an adventurous escape in the deserts, we cover destinations exclusively across India.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-card">
                    <i class="fas fa-star"></i>
                    <h3>Authentic Reviews & Ratings</h3>
                    <p>Genuine feedback from fellow Indian travelers to help you make informed decisions.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-card">
                    <i class="fas fa-handshake"></i>
                    <h3>Host Connect</h3>
                    <p>Communicate directly with hosts to ensure a personalized and seamless experience.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-card">
                    <i class="fas fa-mobile-alt"></i>
                    <h3>Smart & Simple Booking</h3>
                    <p>Easy-to-use platform with secure payment options and instant confirmation.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-card">
                    <i class="fas fa-leaf"></i>
                    <h3>Local Support</h3>
                    <p>By booking through Tripnest, you're supporting local Indian businesses and contributing to the growth of India's tourism economy.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="vision">
            <h2>Our Vision</h2>
            <div class="vision-content">
                <p>To become India's most trusted travel companion by offering tailored stays, celebrating local culture, and encouraging meaningful travel across every state and city in the country.</p>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="why-choose">
            <h2>Why Choose Tripnest?</h2>
            <div class="benefits-grid">
                <div class="benefit-item">
                    <i class="fas fa-flag"></i>
                    <h3>India-First Platform</h3>
                    <p>We focus only on Indian locations and properties.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="benefit-item">
                    <i class="fas fa-store"></i>
                    <h3>Support for Local Businesses</h3>
                    <p>Empowering small and medium hospitality providers.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="benefit-item">
                    <i class="fas fa-heart"></i>
                    <h3>Cultural Connection</h3>
                    <p>Every stay brings you closer to the heart of India.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="benefit-item">
                    <i class="fas fa-headset"></i>
                    <h3>24/7 Customer Support</h3>
                    <p>Based in India, for Indian travelers.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="closing">
            <h2>Let's Rediscover India, Together</h2>
            <p>Whether you're a solo traveler, a couple seeking a romantic getaway, or a family looking for an unforgettable vacation, Tripnest is here to make every journey special.</p>
            <p class="thank-you">Thank you for choosing Tripnest – India's Own Travel Partner.</p>
        </section>
    </div>
</body>